      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on literature precedent for rotating machinery. Sensitivity study comparing Giersiepen and Heuser-Opitz damage laws performed; 12% difference in NIH noted. Achieved level 2 due to absence of higher-fidelity model comparison."
